<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Job Application Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: cadetblue;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .header img {
      max-width: 64px;
      aspect-ratio: 1/1;
    }

    .content {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .content p{
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: #777;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">

      <img src="cid:companyLogo" alt="<%= jobData.companyName %> Logo">

      <h1>Job Application Confirmation</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <%= userName %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for applying for the <strong>
          <%= jobData.jobDesignation %>
        </strong> position at <strong>
          <%= jobData.companyName %>
        </strong>.</p>
      <p>We have received your application and our team will review it shortly. Below are the details of the job you
        applied for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Job Title:</strong>
          <%= jobData.jobDesignation %>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Job Location:</strong>
          <%= jobData.jobLocation %>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Posted Date:</strong>
          <%= jobData.jobPosted %>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>If you have any questions, please feel free to reply to this email.</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>
        <%= jobData.companyName %> Recruitment Team
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %>
          <%= jobData.companyName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>